<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-181-167 </DOCNO><DOCID>10 575 696</DOCID><JOURNAL>Newsbytes  April 9 1991* Full Text COPYRIGHT Newsbytes Inc. 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>New product: fax/copier handles books. (Hitachi Ltd.'s Hit Faxfacsimile distributed by Marshall Industries) (productannouncement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Rohrbough, Linda.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Hitachi Ltd. (Product introduction)Marshall Industries (Marketing).andO;Ticker:    MI; HIT.andO;Product:   Hitachi Hit Fax (Facsimile transceiver) (Product introduction).andO;Topic:     Marketing AgreementsFacsimile Machines.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>NEW PRODUCT: Fax/Copier Handles Books 04/09/91 ELMONTE, CALIFORNIA, U.S.A.,andO;1991 APR 9 (NB) -- The Hit Fax, Hitachi's latest fax product, does notrequire single sheets like other fax machines, but allows faxing of pagesfrom books and manuals, according to Bob Edleman, vice-president of computerproduct marketing for Marshall Industries.andM;&quot;As far as we and Hitachi know, it is the only fax available that does this,&quot;Edleman said.andP;  About the size and appearance of a small copy machine, the HitFax has a glass surface that allows the user to place on the glass thematerial to be faxed.andP;  It also allows the user to use it as a copier, Edlemansaid.andP;  The retail price of the unit is less than $1,000.andM;Other faxes of interest include the Hifax 11 and Hifax L50.andP;  The Hifax 11,for power fax users, includes support for automatic broadcasting to 50locations, tracking of reports for up to 100 departments, memory capability,preset fax time for transmission during lower phone rates, passwordprotection, and stores incoming messages even when it's out of paper,according to Marshall Industries.andP;  The unit's retail price is less than$1,300.andM;The Hifax 50 is a laser fax that uses plain paper, reproduces photographs in`super-gray scale' mode, and will receive and store confidential faxes to beproduced only when a password is entered.andP;  It retails for less than $1,500.andM;Marshall Industries has just become the exclusive industrial distributor forHitachi fax machines.andM;(Linda Rohrbough/19910409/Press Contact: Bob Edleman, Marshall Industries;tel - 818-307-6000, fax - 818-307-6298)</TEXT></DOC>